{"id":27793,"title":"How common medicines can affect bone health.","abstract":"Many people have weak bones and this is a global public health concern. Lifestyle factors can reduce bone density, as can some common drugs. This article describes some of these drugs, the conditions for which they may be prescribed and how they can threaten bone health. Strategies to reduce the risk of fracture and weak bones are outlined.","date":"2014-09-05","categories":"Chemically-Induced Disorders","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25188968","annotations":[{"name":"Drug","weight":0.798721,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drug"},{"name":"Public health","weight":0.787886,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Public_health"},{"name":"Health","weight":0.716476,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Antibacterial","weight":0.70749,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antibacterial"},{"name":"Pharmaceutical drug","weight":0.637607,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pharmaceutical_drug"},{"name":"Bone","weight":0.611415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bone"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.213174,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Fracture","weight":0.199429,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fracture"},{"name":"Bone density","weight":0.0633182,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bone_density"},{"name":"Lifestyle (sociology)","weight":0.0438266,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lifestyle_(sociology)"},{"name":"Global health","weight":0.0301868,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Global_health"},{"name":"State school","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/State_school"},{"name":"Density","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Density"}]}
